data.description: Pride of ownership shows inside and out on this lovely 2 Bdr, 2 Bath home located in the finest gated community of Alder Creek!  Located at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac with views of mature trees and lovingly tended flower beds of roses, hydrangea and more!  As you enter the home, the foyer opens to the expansive Living Room and Dining Room with Vaulted Ceilings giving a very spacious feel.  The gas fireplace and mantle complete the coziness of this home.   Large kitchen with New Stainless Refrigerator and Sink, lots of counter space and cabinets. New wood-look vinyl plank flooring throughout.  Large windows create an abundance of natural light.  Primary suite has double-door access with nicely updated Bathroom, skylight, granite counters on new vanities, easy-step shower and upgraded lighting!  Fresh Interior Paint! Association dues of $237/month covers all landscaping creating a pristine, easy-living yard.  Conveniently located near shopping, medical and golf!
